  <h2 id="overview">Diesel Fuel Centrifuge</h2>

  <p>Rust sediment and sludge from storage tanks contaminate diesel fuel. Condensation in tanks causes water contamination. Alfa Laval diesel centrifuges separate all the solid particles &amp; moisture from diesel fuel.</p>

